      <h2>Pro Cleaning Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Use vinegar and baking soda</strong> to unclog and clean drains naturally.</li>
        <li><strong>Clean top to bottom</strong> – always dust high shelves before the floor.</li>
        <li><strong>Microfiber cloths</strong> pick up dust better than paper towels.</li>
        <li><strong>Use lemon and salt</strong> to clean your garbage disposal and sinks.</li>
        <li><strong>Don’t forget the baseboards!</strong> A quick wipe makes a huge difference.</li>
